{"type":"message","id":"b2a883c4","parentId":"192fe85d","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:50:18.469Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_cf242ba62fae422795d0a127","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"                        <td>前五</td>\n                        <td>性能验证，业界领先</td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>7.4 未来展望</h3>\n            \n            <div class=\"algorithm-box\">\n                <div class=\"algorithm-title\">未来发展方向</div>\n                <ul class=\"feature-list\">\n                    <li><strong>更多开发者采用极简主义框架</strong>：简化开发流程，降低学习成本</li>\n                    <li><strong>AI算法向\"可预测性\"方向发展</strong>：提高AI行为的可预测性和可控性</li>\n                    <li><strong>用户控制权回归</strong>：让用户决定AI的行为和功能</li>\n                    <li><strong>本地AI助手普及</strong>：隐私保护的本地AI助手成为主流</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>结束语</h3>\n            <div class=\"algorithm-box\">\n                <div class=\"algorithm-title\">OpenClaw的价值主张</div>\n                <p>OpenClaw通过创新的算法设计，实现了<span class=\"highlight\">极简、高效、可控</span>的个人AI助手框架。</p>\n                <p>我们相信，未来的AI助手应该是<span class=\"highlight\">本地优先、用户可控、隐私保护</span>的。</p>\n                <p>感谢您的聆听！</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993018460}}
