 3rem; color: var(--text-muted);\">\n                <p>演讲者：[你的名字]</p>\n                <p>日期：2026年3月</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 目录页 -->\n    <section class=\"slide\" id=\"toc\">\n        <div class=\"slide-content\">\n            <h2 class=\"slide-title\">目录</h2>\n            <ul class=\"content-list\" style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">\n                <li>OpenClaw整体架构概览</li>\n                <li>核心控制层Pi的AI算法</li>\n                <li>推理引擎算法</li>\n                <li>工具调用与决策算法</li>\n                <li>记忆系统算法</li>\n                <li>技能系统算法</li>\n                <li>总结与展望</li>\n            </ul>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <!-- 第一部分：OpenClaw整体架构概览 -->\n    <section class=\"slide\" id=\"part1\">\n        <div class=\"slide-content\">\n            <h2 class=\"section-title\">第一部分：OpenClaw整体架构概览</h2>\n            \n            <h3 style=\"color: var(--text-main); margin-top: 2rem;\">1.1 OpenClaw是什么</h3>\n            <ul class=\"content-list\">\n                <li><span class=\"highlight\">本地优先的个人AI助手框架</span></li>\n\n[388 more lines in file. Use offset=200 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993024255}}
