{"type":"message","id":"a64c690b","parentId":"f8f77b12","timestamp":"2026-03-20T07:51:21.427Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_ff3b324ab84c4ec4ace6384e","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    │  2. 编写README文档                      │\n    │     ↓                                   │\n    │  3. 放入技能目录                        │\n    │     ↓                                   │\n    │  4. agent按需加载                       │\n    │     ↓                                   │\n    │  5. 技能调用执行                        │\n    │                                         │\n    └─────────────────────────────────────────┘\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"algorithm-box\">\n                <div class=\"algorithm-title\">Pi的技能扩展方法</div>\n                <ol>\n                    <li><strong>编写CLI工具</strong>：用任意语言编写可执行程序</li>\n                    <li><strong>编写README文档</strong>：描述技能功能和用法</li>\n                    <li><strong>放入技能目录</strong>：将技能文件放到指定目录</li>\n                    <li><strong>agent按需加载</strong>：agent需要时读取技能文档</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>6.2 技能发现算法</h3>\n            \n            <div class=\"algorithm-box\">\n                <div class=\"algorithm-title\">Pi的技能发现方法</div>\n                <p><strong>技能以CLI工具形式存在</strong>：每个技能是一个可执行的命令行程序</p>\n                <p><strong>每个技能有README文档</strong>：描述技能功能、用法和接口</p>\n                <p><strong>agent按需读取技能文档</strong>：需要时才学习技能用法</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 第七部分：总结与展望 -->\n    <div class=\"slide section-slide\" id=\"slide9\">\n        <h2>第七部分：总结与展望</h2>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>7.1 核心算法创新</h3>\n            \n            <div class=\"algorithm-box\">\n                <div class=\"algorithm-title\">五大核心算法创新</div>\n                <ol>\n                    <li><span class=\"highlight\">极简提示词设计</span>（&lt; 1000 tokens）：大幅减少上下文消耗</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"highlight\">状态序列化管理</span>（解决上下文衰减）：支持断点续传</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"highlight\">按需工具加载</span>（大幅降低token消耗）：相比MCP的1/60</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"highlight\">完全可观测推理</span>（避免黑箱操作）：所有过程可见</li>\n                    <li><span class=\"highlight\">探索式上下文收集</span>（基于当前状态工作）：避免过时信息</li>\n                </ol>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"content-section\">\n            <h3>7.2 性能指标</h3>\n            \n            <div class=\"algorithm-box\">\n                <div class=\"algorithm-title\">关键性能指标</div>\n                <table class=\"comparison-table\">\n                    <tr>\n                        <th>指标</th>\n                        <th>数值</th>\n                        <th>说明</th>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>系统提示词</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"highlight\">&lt; 1000 tokens</span></td>\n                        <td>极简设计，大幅减少上下文消耗</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>工具消耗</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"highlight\">225 tokens</span></td>\n                        <td>相比MCP的1/60，效率提升显著</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>GitHub stars</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"highlight\">24,000+</span></td>\n                        <td>社区认可，广泛采用</td>\n                    </tr>\n                    <tr>\n                        <td>Terminal Bench排名</td>\n                        <td><span class=\"highlight\">前五</span></td>\n                        <td>性能验证，业界领先</td>\n                    </tr>\n                </table>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- 结束页 -->\n    <div class=\"slide cover-slide\" id=\"slide10\">\n        <h1>感谢聆听！</h1>\n        <p class=\"subtitle\">OpenClaw AI算法架构深度解读</p>\n        <div class=\"meta-info\">\n            <p>🎉 欢迎交流与讨论</p>\n            <p>📧 OpenClaw - 个人AI助手的未来</p>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n\n[65 more lines in file. Use offset=600 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773993081422}}
